a lightweight, fast, and free web browser

flowRoot.flowPara: The lightweight webkit rendering engine lends Midori the same supremacy in speed that has spurred the growth of Google Chrome.
Midori handles all the latest web technologies like HTML 5 and CSS 3. Listen to music on Rdio, play a game of Angry Birds, and more.
Midori's souce code is freely available for anyone to download and modify, leading to active development and a diverse feature set.
Midori is blazing fast, utilizing the latest web technologies and a small but dexterous array of extensions to provide all the essential features.
"a surprisingly capable browser with a lot of clever design behind it"
"a great browser for those who want to use the Web instead of their browser"
